title: Mike Musto!
description: Mike Musto of Big Muscle is our guest and we talk about the East Coast road trip, twin turbo Gallardos, Orlando, Supras, M3 race cars, Renntech's awesome CLS, and the mini coupe.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
